org.drip.product.calib

Class FloatFloatQuoteSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.product.calib.ProductQuoteSet
      • org.drip.product.calib.FloatFloatQuoteSet

  • public class FloatFloatQuoteSet
extends ProductQuoteSet
    FloatFloatQuoteSet extends the ProductQuoteSet by implementing the Calibration Parameters for the Float-Float Swap Component. Currently it exposes the PV, the Reference Basis, and the Derived Basis Quote Fields.
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
